From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 13:11:51 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 35/73] Wire PDF stream hooks

A PDF knocked politely at the door,
We gave it a stream and a key to the floor.
It still needs a guest to claim its seat,
But the browser-side breadcrumb trail is complete.
